trans-unit.source: Check-In, Take-Off (CITO) is an Erasmus+ project. Erasmus+ projects are funded by the European Commission. Erasmus+ fund organisations across Europe to work and learn together to improve education and training in their individual countries. The CITO project team is comprised of organisations from three countries, Malta, Ireland and Norway; the Directorate for Research, Lifelong Learning and Employability (Malta), the National Adult Literacy Agency (Ireland), Education and Training Boards Ireland (Ireland), Waterford Institute of Technology (Ireland) and Fønix (Norway).
trans-unit.target: Check-In, Take-Off (CITO) huwa proġett tal-Erasmus+. Il-proġetti tal-Erasmus+ huma ffinanzjati mill-Kummissjoni Ewropea. L-Erasmus+ jiffinanzja organizzazzjonijiet madwar l-Ewropa biex jaħdmu u jitgħallmu flimkien biex itejbu l-edukazzjoni u t-taħriġ fil-pajjiżi individwali tagħhom. It-tim tal-proġett ta' CITO huwa magħmul minn organizzazzjonijiet minn tliet pajjiżi, Malta, l-Irlanda u n-Norveġja; id-Direttorat għar-Riċerka, it-Tagħlim Tul il-Ħajja u l-Impjegabbiltà (Malta), in-National Adult Literacy Agency (l-Irlanda), l-Education and Training Boards Ireland (l-Irlanda), il-Waterford Institute of Technology (l-Irlanda) u Fønix (in-Norveġja).

trans-unit.source: We are committed to protecting your privacy in line with the Data Protection Acts 1988 and 2003 and General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) 2018 at all times. This is in line with the Data Protection Acts 1988 and 2003 and General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) 2018.

Aħna mhu se niġbru l-ebda data personali (informazzjoni) dwarek fuq dan is-sit mingħajr il-permess tiegħek jew b'mod ieħor. Dan hu f'konformità mal-Atti dwar il-Protezzjoni tad-Data tal-1988 u l-2003 u r-Regolament Ġenerali dwar il-Protezzjoni tad-Data (GDPR) tal-2018.

trans-unit.source: You do not have to provide us with any personal data to use our site.

trans-unit.source: By simply visiting our site, you do not disclose (share), nor do we collect, personal data about you. The information collected about your visit is limited to technical data like:
trans-unit.target: Jekk sempliċement iżżur is-sit tagħna, int mhux se tikxef, u lanqas m'aħna se niġbru informazzjoni personali dwarek. L-informazzjoni miġbura dwar iż-żjara tiegħek hija limitata għal dik teknika bħal:

trans-unit.source: the Internet address (or IP address) of the device you used to access our site;
trans-unit.target: l-indirizz tal-Internet (jew l-indirizz IP) tal-apparat li int użajt biex taċċessa s-sit tagħna;

trans-unit.source: whether you reached our site using a search engine or if you clicked a link on another website; and
trans-unit.target: jekk wasalt għas-sit tagħna billi użajt magna tat-tiftix jew inkella kklikkjajt ħolqa minn fuq sit web ieħor; u

trans-unit.source: the type of web browser you used and the type of device you used to access the Internet.
trans-unit.target: it-tip ta' brawżer tal-web u t-tip ta' apparat li int użajt biex taċċessa l-Internet.

trans-unit.source: We use technical data for administrative and statistical purposes as well as to help us improve our site. This technical data does not provide us with the personal data of visitors to our site.
trans-unit.target: Aħna nużaw l-informazzjoni teknika għal għanijiet amministrattivi u statistiċi kif ukoll biex tgħinna ntejbu s-sit tagħna. Din l-informazzjoni teknika ma tagħtiniex data personali dwar il-viżitaturi ta' dan is-sit.

trans-unit.source: A cookie is a small piece of data (text file) that a website – when visited by a user – asks your browser to store on your device in order to remember information about you, such as your language preference or login information. Those cookies are set by us and called first-party cookies. More specifically, we use cookies and other tracking technologies for the following purposes:
trans-unit.target: Cookie hija biċċa data żgħira (fajl tat-test) li sit web – meta ssir żjara minn utent – jistaqsi lill-brawżer tiegħek sabiex tinħażen fuq l-apparat tiegħek informazzjoni dwarek, bħal pereżempju l-preferenza tal-lingwa jew l-informazzjoni tad-dħul tiegħek. Dawn il-cookies huma stabbiliti minna u huma msejħa cookies tal-ewwel parti. Aktar speċifikament, aħna nużaw cookies u teknoloġiji ta' traċċar oħrajn għall-għanijiet li ġejjin:

trans-unit.source: These cookies are necessary for the Skills Checker to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you, such as setting your privacy preferences. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but if you do so some parts of the site will not work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.
trans-unit.target: Dawn il-cookies huma meħtieġa sabiex is-CITO Skills Checker jahdem u ma jistgħux jintfew fis-sistemi tagħna. Normalment, dawn jiġu ssettjati skont l-azzjonijiet li int tkun għamilt, bħal pereżempju l-istabbiliment tal-preferenzi ta' privatezza tiegħek. Int tista' tissettja l-brawżer tiegħek biex jimblokka jew javżak dwar dawn il-cookies, iżda jekk tagħmel hekk xi partijiet mis-sit mhux se jaħdmu. Dawn il-cookies ma jaħżnux informazzjoni personali li tidentifikak.

trans-unit.source: These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources (how you ended up on the Skills Checker) so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.
trans-unit.target: Dawn il-cookies jippermettulna ngħoddu ż-żjarat u s-sorsi ta' traffiku (kif wasalt għand is-CITO Skills Checker) ħalli nkunu nistgħu nkejlu u ntejbu l-prestazzjoni tas-sit. Dawn jgħinuna nsiru nafu liema paġni huma l-aktar u l-anqas popolari u naraw kif il-viżitaturi jduru mas-sit. L-informazzjoni kollha li dawn il-cookies jiġbru hija aggregata u għaldaqstant anonima. Jekk int ma tippermettix dawn il-cookies aħna mhux se nkunu nafu meta int żort is-sit tagħna, u mhux se nkunu nistgħu nimmonitorjaw il-prestazzjoni tiegħu.
